Values.value: --Find classification item ID based on Model name, version number and table name Select csai.item_long_nm, csiai.item_nm, csi.cs_item_id, csai.ver_nr cs_ver_nr, csi.item_id csi_item_id, csi.ver_nr csi_item_ver_nr from nci_clsfctn_schm_item csi, admin_item csiai, admin_item csai where csai.item_id = csi.cs_item_id and csai.ver_nr = csi.cs_item_ver_nr and csiai.item_id = csi.item_id and csiai.ver_nr = csi. ver_nr
and csai.ver_nr = %apiParameters/sourceModelVerNr% and upper(csai.item_long_nm) like upper ('%apiParameters/sourceModelName%%%') and upper(csiai.item_nm) = upper('%apiParameters/tableName%')

--Get DataElement Items from classification itemID select b.item_long_nm, perm_val.perm_val_nm, de_conc_item_id, de_conc_ver_nr, de.val_dom_item_id, de.val_dom_ver_nr from de, perm_val, cncpt_admin_item a, admin_item b where (de.item_id, de.ver_nr) in ( select r.c_item_id, r.c_item_ver_nr from nci_clsfctn_schm_item csi , nci_admin_item_rel r where csi.cs_item_id = %de_cs_item_id% and csi.cs_item_ver_nr = %de_cs_item_ver_nr% and csi.item_id = %de_csi_item_id% and csi.ver_nr = %de_csi_item_ver_nr% and csi.item_id = r.p_item_id and csi.ver_nr = r.p_item_ver_nr ) and de.val_dom_item_id = perm_val.val_dom_item_id and perm_val.perm_val_nm = '%apiParameters/attributeValue%' and a.cncpt_item_id = b.item_id and a.item_id = perm_val.NCI_VAL_MEAN_ITEM_ID

select alt.nm_desc ITEMLONG_NM, Decode(Instr(upper(obj_key_desc), 'NAME'), 0 , 'TABLE', 'ATTRIBUTE') ITEM_NM, alt.item_id CS_ITEM_ID, alt.ver_nr CA_VER_NR, '' CSI_ITEM_ID, '' CS_ITEM_VER_NR from alt_nms alt, nci_clsfctn_schm_item csi, nci_admin_item_rel r, obj_key obj where alt.item_id = r.c_item_id and alt.ver_nr = r.c_item_ver_nr and csi.item_id = r.p_item_id and csi.ver_nr = r.p_item_ver_nr and alt.nm_typ_id = obj.obj_key_id and (r.c_item_id, r.c_item_ver_nr) in (select item_id, ver_nr from de where de_conc_item_id = %de_conc_item_id% and de_conc_ver_nr = %de_conc_ver_nr% ) and (csi.cs_item_id, csi.cs_item_ver_nr) in (select item_id, ver_nr from vw_clsfctn_schm where upper(item_nm) like upper('%apiParameters/targetModelName%%%%apiParameters/targetModelVerNr%%%')) order by alt.item_id
